<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-39-0452 </DOCNO><TEXT>The paper concerns Amersham International plc - a high technology companyproviding specialised radioactive products for use in health care, lifesciences research, and industry. A brief description is given of thedevelopment of the company, and the rise in the use of radioisotopesin our present day world. Details of Amersham's medical, industrial andresearch products are given, along with the marketing facilities of theproducts. (U.K.).</TEXT></DOC>